OL,3,CDay centres recommended for closure
OL,4,Cdespite strong opposition
OL,6,FA report has recommended the closure
OL,7,Fof four Adult Social Care Day Centres
OL,8,Fin Birmingham.
OL,10,FMany carers had voiced opposition,
OL,11,Fcalling the plan damaging for
OL,12,Fvulnerable people, particularly those
OL,13,Fwith learning disabilities and autism.
OL,15,FThe decision follows the "Your Day,
OL,16,FYour Say" consultation, which ran from
OL,17,FMay to July 2024.
OL,19,FOver 69% of respondents, including
OL,20,Fcitizens and carers, strongly
OL,21,Fdisagreed with the proposals.
