OL,3,CDay centres recommended for closure
OL,4,Cdespite strong opposition
OL,6,FDespite this, it suggests shutting
OL,7,Ffour day centres - Beeches GOLDD,
OL,8,FFairway, Harborne, and Heartlands.
OL,10,FIt would address a #1.95 million
OL,11,Fbudget gap in 2024-25 and #3.35
OL,12,Fmillion in 2025-26.
OL,14,FCritics argue the closures will
OL,15,Fseverely disrupt the lives of citizens
OL,16,Fwho depend on these centres for
OL,17,Fstability and social interaction.
