OL,3,CDay centres recommended for closure
OL,4,Cdespite strong opposition
OL,6,F"My brother has attended Harborne for
OL,7,Fover 20 years. Moving him would cause
OL,8,Fgreat distress," one carer said,
OL,9,Freflecting widespread concerns about
OL,10,Fthe emotional and mental toll the
OL,11,Frelocations could have on users.
OL,13,FAnother respondent added, "These
OL,14,Fcentres provide vital respite care for
OL,15,Fcarers like myself. Without them, I
OL,16,Fdon't know how we will cope."
