OL,3,CDay centres recommended for closure
OL,4,Cdespite strong opposition
OL,6,FA significant issue raised is the
OL,7,Fincreased travel times resulting from
OL,8,Fthe closures. Citizens, especially in
OL,9,Fthe south of Birmingham, could face up
OL,10,Fto an additional hour of travel each
OL,11,Fway.
OL,13,F"The longer travel will be too much
OL,14,Ffor my father, who is already frail,"
OL,15,Fone citizen shared.
OL,17,FTransport difficulties are compounded
OL,18,Fby the staff shortages that have
OL,19,Fplagued the service, with over 70
OL,20,Fvacancies, including key driver
OL,21,Fpositions.
