OL,3,CDay centres recommended for closure
OL,4,Cdespite strong opposition
OL,6,FMany also criticise the timing and
OL,7,Fapproach of the public consultation,
OL,8,Fclaiming it was insufficient to
OL,9,Fcapture the true scale of the impact.
OL,11,FSome local groups, including the
OL,12,FCentral England Law Centre, have
OL,13,Fquestioned the data used to justify
OL,14,Fthe closures, claiming the council
OL,15,Fdidn't fully consider the lingering
OL,16,Feffects of the COVID-19 pandemic on
OL,17,Fattendance figures.
