OL,3,CDay centres recommended for closure
OL,4,Cdespite strong opposition
OL,6,F"The pandemic drastically changed how
OL,7,Fpeople accessed services, and this
OL,8,Fdecision feels rushed without
OL,9,Facknowledging that reality," one
OL,10,Frepresentative said.
OL,12,FThe council, however, stands by its
OL,13,Fanalysis, citing financial necessity.
OL,15,FIt maintains that the closures will
OL,16,Fresult in improved services at the
OL,17,Fremaining five centres and reiterates
OL,18,Fthat no jobs will be lost in the
OL,19,Fprocess.
