OL,3,CDay centres recommended for closure
OL,4,Cdespite strong opposition
OL,6,FThe council has committed to providing
OL,7,Fcomprehensive support to citizens and
OL,8,Fcarers during the transition, ensuring
OL,9,Ffamiliar staff help ease relocations,
OL,10,Fand offering options such as external
OL,11,FDay Opportunity Services and Direct
OL,12,FPayments.
OL,14,FDespite these assurances, opposition
OL,15,Fremains strong, with many waiting
OL,16,Fanxiously for the council cabinet's
OL,17,Ffinal decision, expected on 15 October.
